    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The inlet boundary condition dataset predates the model revision of 2025-11-14 by approximately three weeks; however, the revision affected only impeller tip clearance geometry downstream of the inlet plane, and the team assessed this change as not material to the boundary condition characterization. No formal re-validation against the revised geometry was performed.",
